snippet.title: [OUT OF LINE] Preview Gameplay w/ Developers and Globku
snippet.description:
◆Wishlist on Steam ⇒ https://bit.ly/3nlZf4w

Out of Line is a 2D sidescroller puzzle platformer adventure, published by Hatinh Interactive and developed by Nerd Monkeys. To be launched in the summer of 2021. 

This is the recording from a live stream at Nerd Monkeys' Twitch channel that was hosted by streamer and youtuber @wearemagicalnoob playing and commenting the preview with the developers.
